title: Economic, Trade & Tech Cooperation Conference opened on Oct. 16 (Hangchou Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Hangchou Municipal Government ) The 17th West Lake Expo kicked off with the Economic, Trade & Tech Cooperation Conference on Oct. 16. The three-day conference will include a number of exhibitions and international cooperation
